      <textAnnotation id="sid-76AAC8FA-7BC5-484D-B0E1-2C0D2874938B" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Cashless settlement – Settlement of Invoices via F110 run without actual movement of funds. This involves use of an In-House Bank center which nets all payments and receipts between IHB participants and converts them to Intercompany loans on which interest is charged/paid.

For Non-Control Countries: Company Codes which have inhouse bank relationship
</text>
      </textAnnotation>
